pageProduct.name: Swisse Vitamin B12 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Vitamin B12 is a premium quality formula to help support energy and red blood cell production, brain and cognitive function, plus immune system health.

Energy Production: Vitamin B12 supports energy production and the metabolism of fats, carbohydrates and protein. It also contributes to the reduction of tiredness and fatigue.

Red Blood Cell Health: Vitamin B12 assists red blood cell production and health.

Brain Health: Vitamin B12 supports brain, nervous system and cognitive function to maintain mental recall and concentration.

Immune Health: Vitamin B12 supports healthy immune system function.

DNA Production: DNA contains our genetic information for the development and function of all cells. Vitamin B12 supports DNA synthesis and production.

Individual Needs: Vegans and vegetarians (or those with limited meat and dairy intake) plus the elderly, may have increased needs for vitamin B12 supplementation.

Size: 60 Tablets

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner.

Ingredients

EACH TABLET CONTAINS: VITAMIN B12 (cyanocobalamin).

VITAMIN B12 (cyanocobalamin) 1000 mcg

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
One tablet daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

One tablet daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
